Image title

President George W. Bush talks with the Chiefs of Staff of the Armed Forces Wednesday, Oct. 24, 2001, after a meeting in the Cabinet Room of the White House. Pictured, from left to right, are Admiral Richard Mies, General Eric Shinseki, General Pete Pace and General Michael Williams. Photo by Eric Draper, Courtesy of the George W. Bush Presidential Library
